Usage : echoto <player> <text>
Restricted to immortal Patrons and above only.

The echoto command takes the text you provide and passes it to the player that
you specify.  The text appears on the screen with no indication who it came
from.  It is just printed there.

Examples:

echoto furball Pinkfish smiles at you.

echoto pinkfish Furball bops you on the head.

echoto ember Pinkfish screams loudly.

echoto shadow Death wanders in and asks you for some advice.
